data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. This is your chance to own in the highly desirable community of  Magnolia Club in Sanford. This 2 bedroom  2 bathroom unit is perfect for a first time homeowner or investor. As you enter, head straight upstairs to revel in the open floor plan with Juliet balconies which boasts plenty of natural light in the living room, seamlessly blending modern living with charm. Enjoy privacy with the split floorpan and a master bedroom that boasts a spacious en suite. Take pleasure in the well maintained community and amenities including the pool, clubhouse, and playground. Conveniently located near Sanford International Airport and major highways, this townhome offers accessibility for travel and entertainment with many local attractions, restaurants, and shopping centers also in close proximity.
